long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The SyntheticEye Chrome extension is designed to empower users in the digital landscape. With advancing AI-generated content, SyntheticEye provides a tool to detect potentially synthetic images, helping users to distinguish AI-generated from real content.

Usage:

Simply activate the SyntheticEye Chrome extension while browsing and upload an image you wish to verify. Choose from our modelsâ€”Aletheia for faces and Argus for general AI-generated images. The image will be evaluated, providing you with a prediction on the likelihood of the image being AI-generated.
